      "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1578985545062-69928b1d9587?w=800&auto=format&fit=crop&q=85",
      "descriptive": true,
      "description": "Every cake at Bakes Bay is baked to order. Classic sponges, fudge-layered chocolates, tiered celebration cakes, custom designs for birthdays, anniversaries, and every quiet occasion worth marking. Share your idea — theme, flavour, dedication — and we'll bake the rest. WhatsApp us to place your order."
